}

IMPORTANT:
- Each scene's audio_text must respect the word limit specified above
- headline_text is an array of short phrases (2-4 words each), or null
- Items array should mirror the items listed above with their exact data
- background_url is always null (will be set separately)
- thumbnail_text should be attention-grabbing and relate to the hook\`;

// Build messages array for Claude
const messages = [
